    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[CodCargo], [s].[CodCedula], [s].[CodSucursal], [s].[CodUnidad], [s].[FechaEntrada], [s].[FechaSalida], [s].[HoraEntrada], [s].[HoraSalida], [s].[IndicadorEntrada], [s].[IndicadorSalida], [s].[NombreCargoEmpleado], [s].[NombreSucursalEmpleado], [s].[NombreUnidadEmpleado], [s].[PrimerApellidoEmpleado], [s].[PrimerNombreEmpleado], [s].[RegistroUsuarioId], [s].[SegundoApellidoEmpleado], [s].[SegundoNombreEmpleado]
    FROM [SegRegistroEmpleados] AS [s]
    ORDER BY [s].[FechaEntrada] DESC, [s].[HoraEntrada] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [s0]
INNER JOIN [AdmEmpleados] AS [a] ON [s0].[CodCedula] = [a].[CodCedula]
LEFT JOIN [AdmCargos] AS [a0] ON [a].[CodCargo] = [a0].[CodCargo]
LEFT JOIN [AdmUnidades] AS [a1] ON [a0].[CodUnidad] = [a1].[CodUnidad]
INNER JOIN [AdmSucursales] AS [a2] ON [s0].[CodSucursal] = [a2].[CodSucursal]
ORDER BY [s0].[FechaEntrada] DESC, [s0].[HoraEntrada] DESC
